    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you cause a psychic disturbance around the target cursed by your @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.VKLPPF5MCCNZ28HP]{Hex} spell. When you do so, you deal psychic damage to the cursed target and each creature of your choice that you can see within 5 feet of it. The psychic damage equals your spellcasting ability modifier (minimum of 1 damage). To use this invocation, you must be able to see the cursed target, and it must be within 30 feet of you.</p>",
